    {
      "id": "p93-CLnBxLw97aOMOEYoD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -18.005538940429688,
      "y": 3422.2999999999993,
      "width": 728.0977172851562,
      "height": 43.2,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6A7fcYOJyZPOrbOaTekW8",
        "jJySN7TCV_8lcNU2QAWE7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2i",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1119507071,
      "version": 585,
      "versionNonce": 1175064511,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775713046340,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    Primitives (int, double, boolean, etc.): यसले सिधै प्रिमिटिभ टाइप लिने मेथड चलाउँछ। यसमा toString() कल हुँदैन, \n            बरु जाभाले आफैँ त्यो नम्बरलाई कन्सोलमा देखाउने सानो मेकानिजम चलाउँछ।",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    Primitives (int, double, boolean, etc.): यसले सिधै प्रिमिटिभ टाइप लिने मेथड चलाउँछ। यसमा toString() कल हुँदैन, \n            बरु जाभाले आफैँ त्यो नम्बरलाई कन्सोलमा देखाउने सानो मेकानिजम चलाउँछ।",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "wTmGvj7KrNwc8XnzYMdx6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3.9944610595703125,
      "y": 3389.8999999999996,
      "width": 894.8500366210938,
      "height": 21.6,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6A7fcYOJyZPOrbOaTekW8",
        "jJySN7TCV_8lcNU2QAWE7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 194101247,
      "version": 356,
      "versionNonce": 1456455647,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775713046340,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "जाभाको PrintStream क्लास (जसको अब्जेक्ट System.out हो) भित्र गोस्लिङले हरेक प्रिमिटिभ टाइपका लागि छुट्टाछुट्टै println मेथडहरू बनाइदिएका छन्।",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "जाभाको PrintStream क्लास (जसको अब्जेक्ट System.out हो) भित्र गोस्लिङले हरेक प्रिमिटिभ टाइपका लागि छुट्टाछुट्टै println मेथडहरू बनाइदिएका छन्।",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "9K5OzEz8HIInGgRzF65Ug",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -21.005538940429688,
      "y": 3471.2528532476836,
      "width": 1082.498291015625,
      "height": 21.247146752316166,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#846358",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6A7fcYOJyZPOrbOaTekW8",
        "jJySN7TCV_8lcNU2QAWE7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2k",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2109464575,
      "version": 471,
      "versionNonce": 2141875199,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775713046340,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    Objects का लागि (String, Student, etc.): यसले public void println(Object x) चलाउँछ। अनि मात्र अघि हामीले कुरा गरेको String.valueOf(x) र x.toString() को खेल सुरु हुन्छ।",
      "fontSize": 15.7386272239379,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    Objects का लागि (String, Student, etc.): यसले public void println(Object x) चलाउँछ। अनि मात्र अघि हामीले कुरा गरेको String.valueOf(x) र x.toString() को खेल सुरु हुन्छ।",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "bKSZphuanSh-NJV3Sgfw1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5.9944610595703125,
      "y": 3499.8999999999996,
      "width": 830.6419067382812,
      "height": 43.2,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4dabf7",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6A7fcYOJyZPOrbOaTekW8",
        "jJySN7TCV_8lcNU2QAWE7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2l",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1869793777,
      "version": 408,
      "versionNonce": 1822069791,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775713046340,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "हरेक पटक सानो int प्रिन्ट गर्दा त्यसलाई Integer अब्जेक्ट बनाउने (Autoboxing), अनि फेरि toString() कल गर्ने गर्दा मेमोरी र समय खेर जान्छ।\n                त्यसैले, Performance राम्रो बनाउन प्रिमिटिभहरूलाई सिधै 'Handle' गर्ने मेकानिजम बनाइयो।",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "हरेक पटक सानो int प्रिन्ट गर्दा त्यसलाई Integer अब्जेक्ट बनाउने (Autoboxing), अनि फेरि toString() कल गर्ने गर्दा मेमोरी र समय खेर जान्छ।\n                त्यसैले, Performance राम्रो बनाउन प्रिमिटिभहरूलाई सिधै 'Handle' गर्ने मेकानिजम बनाइयो।",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
