      "text": "- I is indirect child of Object but direct child \n    of MyParent and if MyParent is direct child of \n    Object class, class I gets all features of\n    Object(grand parent) via its own parent(MyParent)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- I is indirect child of Object but direct child \n    of MyParent and if MyParent is direct child of \n    Object class, class I gets all features of\n    Object(grand parent) via its own parent(MyParent)",
